  <comment>MW deleted "applying;"</comment>
  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="hd_id3155132" role="heading" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="11"><variable id="autoformat"><link href="text/scalc/guide/autoformat.xhp" name="Using AutoFormat for Tables">Applying Automatic Formatting to a Selected Cell Range</link> 
</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149401" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="12">You can use the AutoFormat feature to quickly apply a format to a sheet or a selected cell range.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10702" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">To apply an AutoFormat to a sheet or selected cell range</paragraph>
<list type="ordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN106CE" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select the cells, including the column and row headers, that you want to format.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN106D5" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Choose <item type="menuitem">Format - AutoFormat</item>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3151242" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="27">To select which properties to include in an AutoFormat, click <emph>More</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10715" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Click <emph>OK</emph>.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1075D" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">The format is applied to the selected range of cells.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
<paragraph role="note" id="par_id3149210" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="14">If you do not see any change in color of the cell contents, choose <item type="menuitem">View - Value Highlighting</item>.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_id3155379" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="22">To define an AutoFormat for spreadsheets</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148868" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="26">You can define a new AutoFormat that is available to all spreadsheets.</paragraph>
<list type="ordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3152985" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="23">Format a sheet.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3145384" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="24">Choose <item type="menuitem">Edit - Select All</item>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3153815" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="25">Choose <item type="menuitem">Format - AutoFormat</item>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_idN107A9" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Click <emph>Add</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_idN10760" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">In the <emph>Name</emph> box of the <emph>Add AutoFormat</emph> dialog, enter a name for the format.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_idN107C3" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Click <emph>OK</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
